SkillGate routes and injects skill documents into LLM prompts and
verifies outputs against declared rules. It does not control LLM
behavior directly and does not guarantee that any LLM will comply
with injected instructions. Measured figures in this repository
were obtained under the specific conditions stated alongside them
and do not constitute a guarantee of performance.

